es kann ein Herz ertrain<br />\nEinmal um das andre Mal.<br />\n<br />\nAber weder Lust noch Schmerzen,<br />\nAbgestorben auch der Pein,<br />\nDas ist t&ouml;tlich deinem Herzen,<br />\nUnd so mu&szlig;t du mir nicht sein!<br />\n<br />\nMu&szlig;t dich aus dem Dunkel heben<br />\nW&auml;r es auch um neue Qual!<br />\nLeben mu&szlig;t du, liebes Lebem<br />\nLeben noch dies eine Mal."},{"pid":"f3935b17b16cfc6e8d52d51df687ebc1a681df37","tid":2007393,"uid":210165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T21:33:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7899bd2aaaabb762cead20b7bd447dd6bf583bc","tid":2007393,"uid":300262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"671b857cf82e8fca9f18acbe9a140af61d745215","tid":2007393,"uid":102958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:30:50.000Z","msg":"經歷多啲自然會睇得淡<br />\n都係果句<br />\n可以訴諸於口嘅委屈都唔算委屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T23:13:37.000Z","msg":"真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7aaef5feaf68b4677685b02f28bfd329e530ca2","tid":2007393,"uid":356987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42ba276c5337d944bf6cd7ab9e120dc39f9b6245","tid":2007393,"uid":274021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"究竟點樣先可以令自己變得強大，唔再傷心難過，唔需要其他人，可以好獨立面對任何野，就算一個人都可以好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T00:38:25.000Z","msg":"首先傷心難過係正常既，第二就係人一定係需要其他人，但係唔可以over左，第三就係唔需要好獨立去面對，一個人本身就可以好開心，如果你唔係凝住覺得一個人就好頹既話..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}